{"tid":202262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講左咁耐 的起心肝減肥","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T14:37:42.000Z","uid":93126,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b703ae9011e67ebc16b79a47f4379d043759b242","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"中學起成日話減肥 但次撚次都挨唔過一個禮拜 今次的起心肝減肥<br />\n目標兩個月減到去52kg<br />\n平時做開cd rom 為表決心 決定開post 一但又放棄就比一眾連登仔批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無退路今次實成功<br />\n開始左3日 已經輕左2個斤 希望挨到落去<br />\n會每日推一推post upload下3餐/運動相<br />\n計劃: <br />\n1.戒曬所以甜野同垃圾食物<br />\n2.一星期做最少2-3次運動<br />\n3.少油(目前都白烚緊所有野食)<br />\n4.一星期其中一日係自由日 食自己中意野<br />\n5.遲下諗到再補充或者各位大大比下意見<br />\nps 170絲 62公斤<br />\nbtw 勿相認plz"},{"pid":"c9af9978463f9b82b1787bda00a03a28e89103dc","tid":202262,"uid":60922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都減緊"},{"pid":"f8a36f0bbddb1b49b8f85b541071b4dbbbd9f721","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"15-4-2017<br />\n今日體重<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/12niv8re\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F12niv8re&h=c27af1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日無影到餐飯 呢個係今日menu<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j9c0slob\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj9c0slob&h=1aa35127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kucgxwo0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkucgxwo0&h=0a5af29d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4137d951bbd367b88f501c53575c749029fc76e0","tid":202262,"uid":72989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"絲打努力啊<br />\n肥仔幫推"},{"pid":"5c4f614200355dbd1787a41188ea1f2792d90065","tid":202262,"uid":26709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"戒飯 戒甜 唔好天真要有自由日 少少放縱都足以前功盡棄"},{"pid":"9285d0a62f11c16fe8f880b77e615997be49683e","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒飯 戒甜 唔好天真要有自由日 少少放縱都足以前功盡棄</blockquote><br />\n好似話戒飯會反彈 <br />\n我未減肥前本身其實係食餸多<br />\n飯得幾啖不足半碗份量"},{"pid":"9773433d5e215a840b99fbd10731ec246cf777d5","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"同埋憑勸大家如果減緊肥食得健康但千其唔好食得太少 我係過來人<br />\n真係會反彈得好勁 除非你減完肥仲keep住咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就係咁 兩年前亂減肥之後加上冇恆心戒唔到口太肚餓自暴自棄左<br />\n由56一個月唔夠去到60 近排上埋62kg"},{"pid":"f67196bd0eae0fbcf162a10cee28b2e2f73b6c51","tid":202262,"uid":106081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"絲打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182f9d62e3fe620a820c5d6b2a1c06150c4cf4fd","tid":202262,"uid":7508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"咩apps 黎"},{"pid":"038bd34db197b26ec49119f078eaa36c9c1c771b","tid":202262,"uid":97125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩apps 黎</blockquote><br />\ncalorie counter myfitness pal"},{"pid":"742c676d2cc24f39ac99f6732caa9d933bca405b","tid":202262,"uid":42293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:54:47.000Z","msg":"去旺角請個教練仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643c332256c0cebe2c8a32f866dadbbdc64af7aa","tid":202262,"uid":58925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/225635_acfe5de7ec9dd77d5699d3fbfb43fc7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F225635_acfe5de7ec9dd77d5699d3f