aeb646d0a99ca24e0d458aa","tid":202262,"uid":76158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:24:40.000Z","msg":"我都想減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但太鐘意食嘢，完全開始唔到減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d459d783218dfbc9e60a9fcf04e6245311ead9","tid":202262,"uid":92522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"加油 我都開始左6日 一星期先會上一次磅 因為體重唔重要身型變化先係 有時見到數字減得咁少會好打擊你持久落去 同埋可能關肌肉重左事<br />\n我冇set自由日 因為我驚自己會一日之內爆kcal到痴線 所以我會每日都比個零食quota自己 只限100卡內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時避唔到飯局 就當日另一餐食少d or唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 聽朝度吋數 但我肯定feel到肚腩冇之前咁漲 <span style=\"color: pink;\">153cm 50kg 29&rdquo;肚</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51b3b930cab9b18aa70808b4f063f472d4fa547","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒飯唔會反彈好勁 戒飯=戒糖 主要既糖分都來自飯 如果本身食得少就算 因為我都減緊 係完全戒飯 三餐生果+希臘乳酪 晚餐再加白烚瘦肉同蛋 會反彈個d係冇運動開<br />\n利申 185高 93kg減左幾日去到89kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾日就減左咁多 好挨得但小心身體呀<br />\n巴打都加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91de7145ac62db00d25ad92eb878ca3bee583a50","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但太鐘意食嘢，完全開始唔到減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明呀，我都係好中意食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n減肥係好辛苦但貪靚就要付出代價<br />\n所以減肥要有食係維持身體所需而唔係享受ge觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n減完先食好西都開心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b811ed8695a4b9468d819b95bb08712b7dc755","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"btw唔想當左呢到係fb ig <br />\n我將d 3餐同運動相過番去ig到post<br />\n但大家可以繼續交流減肥心得<br />\n互相勉勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好想瘦<br />\n同埋瘦左係咪個胸會縮水架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664c666af47f6be41c2fcca4de597557a5115549","tid":202262,"uid":68128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"絲打 我162cm 60kg為左靚兩個月前都開始減 唔到肚餓都唔食野 點知而家減到52kg 好似有啲厭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家咩都唔想食"},{"pid":"67e3df5fce704ad0902c201d55c9044016440b65","tid":202262,"uid":93126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油 我都開始左6日 一星期先會上一次磅 因為體重唔重要身型變化先係 有時見到數字減得咁少會好打擊你持久落去 同埋可能關肌肉重左事<br />\n我冇set自由日 因為我驚自己會一日之內爆kcal到痴線 所以我會每日都比個零食quota自己 只限100卡內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時避唔到飯局 就當日另一餐食少d or唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 聽朝度吋數 但我肯定feel到肚腩冇之前咁漲 <span style=\"color: pink;\">153cm 50kg 29&rdquo;肚</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得你都係最主要係要減下個腰圍<br />\n加油 扭多d條腰 同埋做平板幾有用 <br />\n我做左2weeks已經有小小小小線條"}]}